{"tid":2345851,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"今年 除夕倒數•和你嗌 !!!!","createTime":"2020-12-30T00:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T15:58:45.000Z","uid":374427,"like":39,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd368d6b928aaf1a89aa508e1edecf582e35a4a","tid":2345851,"uid":374427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T00:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccXoShX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccXoShX.jpg&h=dc3b1032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n⚠️ 活動：<br />\n<br />\n12.31 除夕倒數&bull;和你嗌<br />\n<br />\n日期：2020年12月31日 (星期四)<br />\n時間：23:50 -- 00:05 <br />\n地點：每個人嘅屋企窗邊<br />\n活動：叫喊口號、一齊倒數迎接2021、<br />\n           踏正12點一齊唱榮光<br />\n<br />\n活動流程：<br />\n23:50 一齊叫喊口號,持續十分鐘 <br />\n23:59 一齊倒數,迎接2021,繼續向前<br />\n00:00 新一年,踏正12點一齊唱榮光<br />\n<br />\n目的：<br />\n1️⃣ 街坊手足互相加油打氣、互相激勵<br />\n2️⃣ 紀念12港人及其他身陷囹吾嘅手足<br />\n3️⃣ 母忘初衷,在新一年繼續為香港奮鬥<br />\n<br />\n==================================<br />\n👉 活動注意事項<br />\n<br />\n⚠️ 本頻道歡迎任何<br />\n      支持民主自由的人參與今次活動<br />\n<br />\n⚠️ 今次活動與David無關<br />\n<br />\n⚠️ 活動期間請留意其他地區哨台,<br />\n  本頻道不會轉發任何狗車/狗隻資訊<br />\n<br />\n⚠️ 今次係和理非活動<br />\n<br />\n=================================="},{"pid":"acbfd370f7a1fc5ba5b232eb3837ecb045e54150","tid":2345851,"uid":374427,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T00:48:15.000Z","msg":"今次活動街都唔使落，喺屋企就得，啱晒驚限聚驚病毒嘅大家!!!!"},{"pid":"8c47187f8f70b42b9184e61ada796c11577a38c8","tid":2345851,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T00:49:26.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n低風險繼續抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18508c652dbbc0b74698d2ca1366e93717492e3","tid":2345851,"uid":374427,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T00:52:47.000Z","msg":"⚠️ 重要呼籲<br />\n<br />\n一.<br />\n<br />\n重有唔夠兩日就到除夕夜啦,<br />\n除夕夜仲未諗到點樣倒數迎接2021？？<br />\n<br />\n不如參加今次嘅和你嗌倒數活動,<br />\n同屋苑/屋邨入面其他街坊手足一齊倒數啦<br />\n🥳🥳🥳🎉🎉🎉🥳🥳🥳🎉🎉🎉<br />\n<br />\n二.<br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得19年除夕夜我地係點倒數嘅呢?!<br />\n今年因為疫情緣故,<br />\n唔可以再好似上年咁聚埋一齊倒數,<br />\n咁就不如喺窗邊同其他街坊手足一齊倒數啦<br />\n🥳🥳🥳🎉🎉🎉🥳🥳🥳🎉🎉🎉<br />\n<br />\n三.<br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得喺19年嘅某段日子,<br />\n每晚10點全港各區都會有街坊手足嘅吶喊聲,<br />\n聽到街坊手足吶喊聲此起彼落,<br />\n彼此互相鼓勵,互相扶持,終有一日定會看見希望<br />\n<br />\n「在晚星墜落徬徨午夜,<br />\n    迷霧裡最遠處吹來號角聲」<br />\n<br />\n🥳🥳🥳🎉🎉🎉🥳🥳🥳🎉🎉🎉<br />\n<br />\n四.<br />\n<br />\n大家一定要記住<br />\n唔係見到希望先去堅持,<br />\n而係堅持先至會見到希望,<br />\n<br />\n大家一定要記住,<br />\n我地係一定唔可以輸俾絕望<br />\n<br />\n就算璀璨奪目嘅香港被黑暗極權所吞噬,<br />\n也始終相信香港終有一天會重光<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入tg channel: <a href=\"http://t.me/resuscitatedhopeinhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fresuscitatedhopeinhk&d=WZfMoUUHHVTN90V%2FD%2BJOGW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=7a9ae33b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/resuscitatedhopeinhk</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8fcc0ca55dd4d14c2315261eee4e1b44915c32","tid":2345851,"uid":4826,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T00:59:16.000Z","msg":"樓主準備比差佬拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af5ea6e1dfae3dc88c3d0b7c7f64e29d028a6f9","tid":2345851,"uid":374427,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c47187f8f70b42b9184e61ada796c11577a38c8","tid":2345851,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T00:49:26.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n低風險繼續抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T01:20:02.000Z","msg":"幫手share開去 pleaseeeee 🙇&zwj;♂️🙇&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"b89b2aad0355956249d5ee02f49cc18bb563c891","tid":2345851,"uid":309558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T01:33:3